      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZULU YALLAH (8) has a terrific record this track and trip with 10 wins and two placings from 12 starts. Comes off a (22.36) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a OPEN over 400m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. MAILATA (1) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (22.58) at this track in a OPEN over 400m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Must be included in calculations. LET ME COOK (2) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5.5 lengths into second (22.75) at this track in a OPEN over 400m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Hard to beat again. ACTION SHOT (3) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
